            </form>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
                        
                        <p>Municipal water should be better taken care of and should use these high-tech <a href="https://www.citylab.com/life/2015/02/the-single-best-reason-that-boxed-water-is-better/385138/" target="_blank">water filtration systems</a> used by the convenience water companies, and thus, the market for convenience water should be erased. Everyone should have access to free, safe, potable tap water.&nbsp;</p>
<p><em>Sophie Laettner is a Trinity senior. Her column, “better laettner than never,” typically runs on alternate Fridays.</em></p>

